cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC 

This paper involves the use of robots to assist people in bed, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also uses convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) to estimate 3D joint positions of a person from a single pressure image, which involves computer vision techniques. The use of neural networks also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the potential healthcare applications of the technology, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
